Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.10,0:16:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离够吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.24,0:16:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会全力试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.68,0:16:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 你要用那个对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.42,0:16:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太危险了 不行!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.28,0:16:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.55,0:17:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员 开始掩护!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.65,0:17:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.77,0:17:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.13,0:17:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.39,0:17:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她要干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.78,0:17:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.97,0:18:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.51,0:18:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.86,0:18:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.12,0:18:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.04,0:18:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了 摧毁了一门
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.70,0:18:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伍 伍德 发生了什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.45,0:18:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炮弹不知为什么在空中爆炸 被爆炸波及了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.35,0:18:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我亲爱的伍德...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.09,0:19:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会为你复仇的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.04,0:19:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用剩下的普林炸飞加利亚的垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.01,0:19:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.69,0:19:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.42,0:19:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.82,0:19:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.08,0:19:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦尔基里之光啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.10,0:19:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要怕 那不是能多次发射的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.16,0:19:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然已经用过了 现在一定能打垮他们!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.41,0:19:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要保持清醒 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.96,0:19:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.95,0:19:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.87,0:19:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边还有一门巨炮呢 我们要被消磨死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.48,0:20:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是古斯鲁古
