Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.66,0:25:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 只是护送小美女啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.53,0:25:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能让女孩子和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.40,0:25:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.15,0:25:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战壕就是血管
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.55,0:25:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里受伤了就往那里运送白血球
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.52,0:25:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀死入侵的细菌!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.40,0:25:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟上!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.52,0:26:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被发现了!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.32,0:26:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.58,0:26:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是没事...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.88,0:26:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是炸药...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.89,0:26:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么猛烈的弹幕 有几条命也拿不会来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.40,0:26:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普林 发射准备完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.91,0:26:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十 九 八 七 六 五
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.04,0:26:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.32,0:26:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 方位不变
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.29,0:27:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方位不变 距离修正20
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.52,0:27:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解 距离修正20
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.50,0:27:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预备 发射!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.22,0:27:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BINGO!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.63,0:27:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中了!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.29,0:27:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的伍德...我的普林...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.85,0:27:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨炮被摧毁了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.02,0:27:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就不需要炸药了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.74,0:27:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缪希汉森司令!伊莎还在...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.43,0:27:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维修中也无所谓 发射一炮还是没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.08,0:27:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们来炸碎那些躲在树林里开炮的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.51,0:27:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
