Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.71,0:28:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,观测兵!确定森林里敌军的位置!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.00,0:28:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.30,0:28:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉艾拉 你还不能动
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.69,0:28:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.84,0:28:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉艾拉 枪我借一下 我要狙击观测兵
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.22,0:28:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这枪不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.85,0:28:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行也得行!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.20,0:28:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉艾拉!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.13,0:28:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.56,0:28:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才你保护了我 这次轮到我保护你了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.34,0:29:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库鲁特 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.30,0:29:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.41,0:29:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.35,0:29:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 彻底打扫一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.58,0:29:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一发反坦克弹 怎么打扫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.56,0:29:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我好了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.50,0:29:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加利亚的渣滓们 竟敢把我的女儿们...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.79,0:29:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.21,0:30:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 干掉三辆
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.41,0:30:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没了炸药怎么摧毁那门大炮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.14,0:30:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点给我装填!!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.77,0:30:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能试试了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.54,0:30:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 莫非你想一个人...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.95,0:30:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊姆卡!!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.04,0:30:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别拦她
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.13,0:30:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是..
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.33,0:30:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.12,0:30:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.10,0:30:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.19,0:31:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的女儿们啊!!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.04,0:31:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.08,0:31:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.51,0:31:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊姆卡她们成功了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.35,0:32:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次真的作战终了了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.50,0:32:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.44,0:32:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.73,0:32:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的台词
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.46,0:32:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然在这么短的时间里逆转了战局
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.80,0:32:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害的部队啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.49,0:32:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 可是我...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.23,0:32:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连他们的名字都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.25,0:32:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前进!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.15,0:32:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正规军的那群家伙终于开始攻势了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.71,0:32:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是会捡便宜
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.11,0:32:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们422部队的功劳我们都很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.13,0:32:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.88,0:32:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桥头堡被攻陷了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.79,0:32:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然啊 那个叫缪希汉森的家伙根本不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.49,0:32:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 他应该是位优秀的指挥官吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.60,0:32:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.51,0:33:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了他我们才能全身而退的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.32,0:33:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼哼 那么...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.62,0:33:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,返回我们的战场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.19,0:33:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少了一个落脚点而已 这点损失不算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.82,0:33:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.49,0:33:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说蒂尔斯伯格桥头堡被攻陷了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.37,0:33:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我出战的话可以一举扭转战局
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.21,0:33:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退下
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.62,0:33:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.12,0:33:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 塞露贝莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.31,0:33:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快到你出场了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.80,0:33:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马克西米利安大人...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.54,0:34:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次我们去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.80,0:34:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.01,0:34:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过肯定有人在等着我们的帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.51,0:34:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的战斗 没有终点
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.99,0:34:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对



