Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.25,0:01:27.90,opch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}明天又会被夺走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
